OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FTowie star Chloe Lewis has paid
OL,7,Ftribute to her "first love" and
OL,8,F"childhood sweetheart" Jake Hall after
OL,9,Fhe died earlier this month, aged 35.
OL,11,FThe former couple started dating when
OL,12,Fthey were teenagers and their on-off
OL,13,Frelationship was documented in reality
OL,14,FTV series The Only Way Is Essex. They
OL,15,Fbroke up for good in 2016.
OL,17,FHall, 35, died from head injuries at a
OL,18,Fvilla in Majorca, Spain, on May 6.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
