OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FLewis, 35, wrote that Hall was the
OL,12,F"most talented and creative person I
OL,13,Fknew" who always had the "purest heart
OL,14,Fand the greatest soul" as she shared a
OL,15,Fmontage of photos and videos of them
OL,16,Ftogether on Instagram.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
