OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FShe recalled meeting Hall at a bar
OL,7,Faged 16, stating that he looked like
OL,8,Fhe had "stepped straight out of a
OL,9,FRalph Lauren" with his sleeves rolled
OL,10,Fup and a red sweatshirt tied over his
OL,11,Fshoulders.
OL,13,F"I remember thinking, how am I stuck
OL,14,Fwith this guy for the night? But
OL,15,Fsomehow, you danced with me all night
OL,16,Fand we belly-laughed until the early
OL,17,Fhours," Lewis said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,F"You made me feel like I was the most
OL,7,Fwonderful person you had ever met.
OL,8,FFrom that day on, we were inseparable,
OL,9,Fand you became my best friend."
OL,11,FLewis, a mum-of-one, described Hall as
OL,12,Fa "massive and special part of my
OL,13,Flife" and said she wished he could
OL,14,Fhave seen "just how deeply" he was
OL,15,Floved.
OL,17,FHall was best known for his almost
OL,18,Fdecade-long stint on Towie, having
OL,19,Fjoined in 2015 and quit in 2024.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
