OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FHe was also an artist, as well as
OL,7,Frunning the menswear brand called By
OL,8,FJake Hall.
OL,10,FHall leaves behind one daughter,
OL,11,FRiver, with his ex, Misse Beqiri, who
OL,12,Fhas appeared on the Real Housewives of
OL,13,FCheshire.
OL,15,FRead Lewis' tribute to Hall in full
OL,16,Fbelow.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
