OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FMy first love, my childhood
OL,7,Fsweetheart. A love that taught me so
OL,8,Fmuch about life and myself, and even
OL,9,Fmore so now your presence is no longer
OL,10,Fhere.
OL,12,FA complete pain in the arse most of
OL,13,Fthe time, but always with the purest
OL,14,Fheart and the greatest soul. You
OL,15,Ftouched so many lives and meant well
OL,16,Fin everything you did.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
