OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FI knew who you were... and I know what
OL,7,Fyou wanted from life... a happy home
OL,8,Fand a loving family. Being the best
OL,9,Fdad was the most important thing to
OL,10,Fyou & we always use to speak about it.
OL,12,FYou did that, Jake, with pride and
OL,13,Fmade it look so easy and effortless.
OL,14,FLike I knew you would.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
