OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FWe met at the age of 16, when you
OL,7,Fstalked me in a bar and ended up
OL,8,Fcoming out with my sister and Danny
OL,9,Ffor the night. You looked like you had
OL,10,Fstepped straight out of a Ralph Lauren
OL,11,Fcatalogue in your shirt, sleeves
OL,12,Frolled up, with a red sweatshirt tied
OL,13,Fover your shoulders like a little
OL,14,FSpanish boy.
OL,16,FI remember thinking, How am I stuck
OL,17,Fwith this guy for the night? But
OL,18,Fsomehow, you danced with me all night
OL,19,Fand we belly-laughed until the early
OL,20,Fhours.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
