OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FYou made me feel like I was the most
OL,7,Fwonderful person you had ever met.
OL,8,FFrom that day on, we were inseparable,
OL,9,Fand you became my best friend.
OL,11,FNavigating our young years and being
OL,12,Fthrown into a reality TV show, being
OL,13,Fin the public eye wasn't really what
OL,14,Fwe wanted, but it all just happened so
OL,15,Fquickly & it took over our
OL,16,Frelationship. It was a huge struggle
OL,17,Ffor me & mentally hurt us both.
OL,19,FWe had our ups and downs, but we
OL,20,Falways knew how to come back to each
OL,21,Fother... until it was all too late.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
