PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FLife got in the way, and we separated
OL,7,Fafter spending 10 years together. We
OL,8,Fdidn't love wrong, we just didn't know
OL,9,Fhow to hold on to it.
OL,11,FThe most talented and creative person
OL,12,FI knew, from such a young age `
OL,13,Fstarting Prevu in your mum and dad's
OL,14,Fgarage. Me and Mummy were always your
OL,15,FNo.1 fans.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
