OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FYou came up with the most gorgeous
OL,7,Fstyles that were completely original,
OL,8,Fand I remember the day you made me the
OL,9,Ffirst womenswear piece and insisted on
OL,10,Ftaking photos of me wearing it. It was
OL,11,Funique, just like you.
OL,13,FYou loved music the way it should be
OL,14,Floved, and the words to so many songs
OL,15,Fmean so much more now. I'll never
OL,16,Fforget the moment you sang "Ordinary
OL,17,FPeople" to me for the first time, and
OL,18,Fit will forever be our song.
OL,26,@xD@\OUyD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/16
