OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FSitting at your laptop, smiling at me
OL,7,Fwhile singing, "Girl, I'm in love with
OL,8,Fyou..." with your cheeky smile and
OL,9,Flove in your eyes. The best kind of
OL,10,FJake.
OL,12,FYou were a pest and drove the people
OL,13,Fwho cared about you crazy, but we
OL,14,Floved you, and I wouldn't have changed
OL,15,Fyou for the world.
OL,26,@oD@POUpD@GO]
