PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FThe last few weeks have felt very
OL,7,Fsurreal, and I still don't really know
OL,8,Fhow to process you being gone. I last
OL,9,Fsaw you in February 14th when I told
OL,10,Fyou to take care of yourself. But you
OL,11,Fnever listened, did you? You always
OL,12,Fdid it your way.
OL,14,FYou were such a massive and special
OL,15,Fpart of my life, and I truly hoped
OL,16,Fthat we would grow old, that I'd see
OL,17,Fyou one day, happy and at peace with
OL,18,Flife. We'd smile at each other and be
OL,19,Fgrateful that life had been good to us.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FBut now I know that God had better
OL,7,Fplans for you.
OL,9,FHeartache echoes through the world for
OL,10,Fyou Jake. I've never seen so many
OL,11,Fpeople pour their love out for one
OL,12,Fperson.
OL,14,FI wish you could see it all ` to
OL,15,Frealise just how deeply you were
OL,16,Floved. I hope you can now, and that
OL,17,Fyour mind is finally peaceful.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/16
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
