PN,30615
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1780081925
OL,3,CTowie's Chloe Lewis shares moving
OL,4,Ctribute to 'first love' Jake Hall
OL,6,FYou'll be in my thoughts forever, and
OL,7,FI'm sorry I couldn't have saved you.
OL,8,F'The world feels quieter since you've
OL,9,Fbeen gone, like somehow all the music
OL,10,Fis all wrong.'
OL,12,FI hope it's peaceful up there, and I
OL,13,Freally hope that one day I get to see
OL,14,Fyou again. Keep shining like you
OL,15,Falways do. Stay Magic.
OL,17,FQue Sera, Sera, Jakey.
OL,19,FAll my love Always
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/16
